Important guidelines:
- Create specific, actionable tasks
- Use actual tool/workflow IDs from the available lists
- Set proper dependencies to ensure correct execution order
- Include all necessary parameters for tool/workflow execution
- Add memory storage tasks for important learned information
- Consider adding context search tasks when more information is needed
